{
  "info": {
    "name": "闪购秒杀系统 · 全链路E2E测试（含异常场景）",
    "description": "覆盖正常路径+异常场景。导入后按文件夹顺序执行。每个请求均有断言，一键运行自动判断成败。\n\n使用方式：\n1. Import to Postman\n2. 按文件夹顺序执行（0-管理员准备 → 1-用户管理 → 2-商品 → 3-地址 → 4-购物车 → 5-订单 → 6-秒杀 → 7-AI → 8-管理）\n3. 如需并发测试：newman run collection.json -d data.csv -n 10",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url", "value": "http://localhost:8080" },
    { "key": "token", "value": "" },
    { "key": "userId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "productId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "addressId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "cartId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "orderId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "activityId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "adminToken", "value": "" },
    { "key": "testUser", "value": "" },
    { "key": "testUser2", "value": "" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "0-管理员准备",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "管理员登录",
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": {
              "exec": [
                "const json = pm.response.json();",
                "pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.eql(200);",
                "pm.expect(json.code).to.eql(0);",
                "pm.expect(json.data.token).to.not.be.empty;",
                "pm.expect(json.data.userId).to.be.a('number');",
                "pm.collectionVariables.set('adminToken', json.data.token);",
                "pm.collectionVariables.set('userId', String(json.data.userId));"
              ],
              "type": "text/javascript"
            }
          }],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{\"username\":\"admin\",\"password\":\"admin123\"}"},
            "url": {"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/user/login", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","user","login"]}
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "获取商品列表（取第一个商品ID）",
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": {
              "exec": [
                "const json = pm.response.json();",
                "pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.eql(200);",
                "pm.expect(json.code).to.eql(0);",
                "pm.expect(json.data.records).to.be.an('array').that.is.not.empty;",
                "pm.collectionVariables.set('productId', String(json.data.records[0].id));"
              ],
              "type": "text/javascript"
            }
          }],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{"key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}"}],
            "url": {"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/product?page=1&size=10", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","product"], "query": [{"key":"page","value":"1"},{"key":"size","value":"10"}]}
          }
        }
      ]
    },
